{
  "name": "VIPER — Daily Competitor Intelligence Monitor",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# 🐍 VIPER\n## Daily Competitor Intelligence Monitor\n\nRuns every **day at 6AM UTC**\n\n**What VIPER tracks:**\n• Competitor product launches & feature updates\n• Competitor pricing changes & positioning shifts\n• Industry news mentioning key competitors\n• New entrants in the AI automation market\n• Social & community buzz about competitors\n• Flags anything significant for immediate attention\n\n**Alert threshold:** Only notifies when genuinely new intelligence is found — no noise.",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 360,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "viper-sticky-overview",
      "name": "Sticky Note — Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-80, 80]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ⏰ TRIGGER\n**Every Day**\n**6:00 AM UTC**\n\nDaily cadence catches\ncompetitor moves within\n24 hours of happening.",
        "height": 160,
        "width": 200,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "viper-sticky-trigger",
      "name": "Sticky Note — Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [320, 80]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🧠 AI ANALYST\n**Claude via OpenRouter**\n\nReads all competitor\nresearch, compares to\nprevious log, identifies\nwhat is NEW vs already\nknown. Only flags\ngenuine new signals.",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 220,
        "color": 7
      },
      "id": "viper-sticky-agent",
      "name": "Sticky Note — Agent",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [600, 80]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔍 MONITORING TOOLS\n\n1. **Competitor News** — Latest press & announcements\n2. **Product Launches** — New features, tools, pricing\n3. **Social Signals** — What people say about competitors\n4. **Market Entrants** — New players in the space\n5. **Log Reader** — Previous intel for deduplication",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 280,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "viper-sticky-tools",
      "name": "Sticky Note — Tools",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [900, 80]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🚨 ALERT OUTPUT\n\n• Log all findings\n  to Google Sheets\n• Email alert only\n  when NEW intel found\n\nNo alert = nothing\nsignificant happened.",
        "height": 180,
        "width": 200,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "viper-sticky-output",
      "name": "Sticky Note — Output",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1280, 80]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 6 * * *"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "viper-trigger",
      "name": "Every Day 6AM UTC",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [320, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "systemMessage": "You are VIPER, RemShield's autonomous competitor intelligence monitor. Every morning you scan the competitive landscape for AI engineering and automation services.\n\nKey competitors to monitor:\n- Make (formerly Integromat) — no-code automation\n- Zapier — workflow automation\n- Relevance AI — AI agent builders\n- Bardeen AI — browser automation\n- n8n Cloud — self-hosted automation competitors\n- Any new AI automation agencies or studios gaining traction\n\nYour daily intelligence mission:\n1. Search for latest news about key competitors (product launches, pricing, partnerships, funding)\n2. Find any new competitor products or feature launches in AI automation\n3. Check what communities are saying about competitors (sentiment, complaints, praise)\n4. Look for new entrants in the AI engineering services market\n5. Read the previous monitoring log to avoid reporting old news\n6. Assess: is there anything GENUINELY NEW and significant today?\n7. Save your findings to the intelligence log\n8. Only send an email alert if there is real new intelligence worth flagging\n\nBe concise. Flag only what matters. Include source URLs for every finding.",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "viper-agent",
      "name": "VIPER Intelligence Agent",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 1.7,
      "position": [640, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-5",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "viper-llm",
      "name": "Claude via OpenRouter",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatOpenRouter",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [640, 560],
      "credentials": {
        "openRouterApi": {
          "id": "XCN7CrgU2LltzECD",
          "name": "GP1"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
